data.name: label1.Text
data.value: You are a crew member of The "Nostromo" cargo spaceship. You are heading to Solar system. Your mission is to deliver extremely valuable cargo to the space station on Enceladus, Saturn's moon. Information about the cargo is classified. The ship is on its way from the Proxima Centauri star system. The distance to Enceladus is 4 light years. The ship is in automatic mode, and the crew is immersed in a stasis sleep.
